  "body": "Hi team,\r\n\r\nLecky from Swell team here, during our guarded launch stage 1 we have noticed an edge case issue that 2 of our validators got stuck from activation with balance 32 and effective balance 31. \r\n\r\nValidator 1:\r\nhttps://beaconcha.in/validator/b6c1531b7896e3493806a8dd72fa9c3387f4f7a2fdc565bf1e8e66becb0666f8c3938270a757703e3865619dcc34bf7c#deposits\r\nValidator 2:\r\n[https://beaconcha.in/validator/8a4f2e7e2fea00a9ce77d669aeba2573137010db2f85e18c0265e492d3a9b5367e15f356abd58b2bfb3a3bddef9aece9#deposits](https://beaconcha.in/validator/b6c1531b7896e3493806a8dd72fa9c3387f4f7a2fdc565bf1e8e66becb0666f8c3938270a757703e3865619dcc34bf7c#deposits)\r\n\r\nMore context [here](https://blog.swellnetwork.io/swell-network-guarded-launch-update). \r\n\r\nThe root cause for the edge case is hysteresis applies global delta regardless of validator status, however it's not necessary to apply that on a pending validator.",
